Create objects.

    oc create -f deploy.yaml

Replace volume.

    oc set volume deploymentconfig/synapse --add \
        --name synapse --overwrite \
        --type persistentVolumeClaim --claim-name matrix

Build.

    oc start-build --follow synapse

Deploy.

    oc rollout latest deploymentconfig/synapse

Create route.

    oc create route edge \
        --hostname matrix.example.com \
        --service synapse
    oc annotate route synapse \
        --overwrite haproxy.router.openshift.io/timeout=1m
